I love you mikey and i miss you much<3

So things have been really crazy in the family life lately. Insane mess has been going on. This shit is so dumb. I Dont feel like puttin my personal shit out so yeah. 

There's this boy, we'll call him bobby and this girl, well she can be sally, and then there is me. Sally likes bobby but bobby likes me. WTF?? are we in the 2nd grade or what??? This is why i dont chill with you anymore. You cause way to much drama. We just started hanging out last weekend and already you wanna " kill " me. Well ya know what bring it cuz i wish you would step up and do something. Dont talk shit about me to anyone else you got something to say about me then grow some damn balls and tell me to my face. Or are you SCARED??? ha. what a joke, like you could be realistic about something. Mature. Riiiiite. NEWS FLASH: NICOLE NEEDS TO SNAP BACK TO REALITY!!

Anyways..went to the bowling alley tontie. that was fun. Wrote cassie's number on a light pole and sed " for a good time call" haha. it was so much fun. dont give me ideas, specially if i got a sharpie with me!! :-) I love you girl!! 

Crashing at Heather's for the nite. like usual. Anyways....Play tomorrow at like 1 then Hockey game at Chilled Ponds at 5:40 then <3 Jason's house <3 afterwards. Should be fun!! Me Heather & Tanya and JASON and some of his friends...deff should be interesting. 



MIKEY: Babe i love you so much and i cant wait til you come home. Im really sorry about everything. Im here for you babe. I miss you much and i love you much too. Ill be checkin that email tomorrow. :-) SEALED WITH A KISS ALWAYS AND FOREVER :-*  Cant wait to see ya. ;-)

DONT LET IT GO TO YOUR HEAD!!! YOu aren't that great to begin with.

Everyone always wants to ruin the things i want the most in life. 

Today was a horrible day. It was just one of those days where nothing goes rite and people tell you EVERYTHING you dont wanna hear. IT SUCKED!! 

I dont care what people say about JaSoN, i still wanna take that risk. Fuck everyone else.

Things lately have deff been confusing. I mean from old friends to new ones and from guys to other NEW guys....its just been one of those weeks ya know? 

Okay so there is this guy i kinda sorta a little bit like. He is cool and really sweet and all but he is the trouble maker kind. I mean i dont mind a bad boy....as long as it doesnt affect me. I like him tho but he has a girlfriend. He says he will break up with her for me but i dont know. In some ways that just seems wrong. I just wouldnt feel rite. But then another part of me says...well if he is gonna end it with her for me atleast you know who he likes rite?? well i dont know. I mean he is really sweet to me which no one seems to believe because of who it is but he IS!! haha. I guess i will just have to see what happens with us. i dont know.

Life rite now is good i guess you could say. Things are going decent for once. Same ol shit everyday tho thats prolly why. I feel the need to cause a little trouble ya know?? I just feel like doing something i know is wrong just for the hell of it! haha. well yeah neways....

Mikey is coming home next month. THANK GOD!! i miss him so much. NICOLE AND MIKEYS HUGE ADVENTURE....coming soon!! hehe. I LOVE YOU BABY!! <3

Well....that's all folks!!! later



:) --,--------'----------@      LOVE ALWAYS


NICOLE AKA NICKI

And on top of that, for me to of let things go as far as they did and then for you to do this shit!! What the hell was i thinking. Things never change with me....i always go for the assholes. No matter how much people warn me i just dont fuckin listen. Ga-Ah!!! I just wish for once things would work for me. Everyone thinks i lead this o so happy life....not everything is all good and gravy in NicoleLand! when one thing happens a bunch of shit happens. And everyone wonders why i always seem depressed and mad or whatever. My mom wonders why i have an attitude....maybe cuz right now it seems like everything is falling apart in my world. I mean dont get me wrong cuz i know other people elsewhere have it ALOT worse than me or whatever im just saying. Everyone thinks they know but they dont. They dont have a fuckin clue. 

To all my friends who love me and care about me: I love you all more than words can say. I know we have all had our ups and downs but we have gotten through them and im glad i have all of you. Thanks so much for always being there for me and listening to me. <3333 xxoo I LOVE YOU ALL!!!!!!

TODAY-went to school like usual. Had a bunch of fun in 3rd block...that's drama class. Then stayed back for a drama club meeting and stage crew meeting. Stage Crew was a BLAST!!! We played hockey in the hall with a bottle of frozen water and a pipe stick thingy thing. It was fun!!!! Today was the best day of school yet!!!! <333

Well i guss that's all i got to say for now. Catch ya'll on the flip side!!!!
